  Te7 11 chiuN <BR>  Kim e5 Pio2-a2 
  Te7 ji7 jit8, Heng5-su7 chhut-goa7 choe3 kang, Kat-la-ti2 chhut khi3 khioh chha5, Sou Pek-hok khi2-lai5 che7 ti7 kau-i2 nih8, Pek chim2 siu-cheng2 pang5-lai7, sau3 toe7 liau2 chiu7 chiong liu2-chhiu7 piN kut-tioh8 gun5 e5 su7, soe3-ji7 kong2 hou7 i thiaN. Pek peh thiaN liau2, chap8 hun e5 hoaN-hi2, cheng-sin5 toa7 chin2-heng, au7-lai5 koh chiong kim pio2-a2 theh8 chhut lai5, theh8 hou7 i e5 tiong7-hu, ng3-bang7 i e5 tiong7-hu ka7 i kong2 pio2-a2 e5 goan5-in,i e5 tiong7-hu theh8 pio2-a2 khoaN3 chit8 tiap-a2-ku2 kong2, “U7 iaN2, goa2 oe7-ki3-tit chheng-chheng chho2-chho2 e5, u7 chit8 e5 chin ho2 e5 ta-pou gin2-na2, chhin-chhiuN7 lan2 Heng5-su7 chit8 iuN7 e5 seng5-sit8, i ti7 goa2 be7 poah8-to2 hit jit8 e5 i2-cheng5 hou7 goa2.” I e5 tiong7-hu kong2 chit e5 oe7 e5 si5 bin7-sek pian3-peh8, siaN-im hoat chun3, Pek chim2 kin2 theh8 tam7-poh8 ioh8 lai5 hou7 i chiah8, i chiu7 khah ho2, ke3 chit8 khek ku2, Pek chim2 koh mng7, “Hit e5 gin2-na2 chaiN2-iuN7 hou7 li2 chit e5 pio2-a2 ?” 
