  Pek chim2 koh mng7, “Li2 oe7-ki3-tit i e5 pe7 e5 mia5, peng3 tiam3 ti7 tah-loh8 mah ?” 
  In3 kong2, “Goa2 boe7-ki3-tit, goa2 chin7-lat8 siuN7 i e5 lau7-pe7 e5 mia5-siN3 chu7-chi2, koh siuN7 i to5-chau2 kau3 tah-loh8 chit8 kok, goa2 choan5-jian5 siuN7 boe7 chhut-lai5, chi2-u7 chai thau5-nau2 loan7-loan7 chhin-chhiuN7 toa7 hai2-chui2 hoa7-hoa7 hau2 e5 siaN-im, na2 chhin-chhiuN7 te7-hoaN7 to2 chit8 iuN7.” 
