  Pek chim2 chiu7 kin2-kin2 kong2, “Kiam2-chhai2 Phok i-seng oe7 bat chit kui2 ji7 e5 i3-su3.” Chit8 bin7 kong2, chit8 bin7 chiong pio2-a2 theh8 hou7 Phok i-seng khoaN3. I-seng chit8 e7 khoaN3 hit e5 L.J.P. saN ji7 boe7 bian2 toa7 kiaN, chiu7 a-a khau3 kong2, “Chit e5 si7 goa2 e5 kiaN2 e5 mia5-ji7, li2 kong2 hit e5 gin2-na2 un2-tang3 si7 goa2 e5 kiaN2.” Sui5-si5 khau3 kio3 kong2, “Goa2 e5 kiaN2 La-jin5-su ah, Goa2 taN oe7 chai li2 ti7 tah-loh8 chiu7 ho2, goa2 e5 Siong7-te3 ah, chit si5 i tek-khak ti7 hia teh kan-khou2, kiam2-chhai2 si7 si2 lah, ia7 be7 thang chai, Pek peh, goa2 e5 kiaN2 u7 kio3 goa2 kia3 phoe hou7 i mah ?” 
